data.name: ResultSetType
desc: describes the different scroll capabilities of a result set.

items.name: FORWARD_ONLY
lines: is the type for a com.sun.star.sdb.ResultSet object whose cursor may move only forward.

items.name: SCROLL_INSENSITIVE
lines: is the type for a com.sun.star.sdb.ResultSet object that is scrollable but generally not sensitive to changes made by others.

items.name: SCROLL_SENSITIVE
lines: is the type for a com.sun.star.sdb.ResultSet object that is scrollable and generally sensitive to changes made by others.
